Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.70,0:03:11.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才能發送D-MAIL嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.58,0:03:13.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的確說得通
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.16,0:03:15.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別這麼大聲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.00,0:03:15.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喊得我頭痛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.91,0:03:17.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.08,0:03:19.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mr.顯像管這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.29,0:03:22.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到會暴力相向…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.46,0:03:24.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這就是活該
